name: FunLimericks
0:
”Alexa, ask Fun Limericks to tell me a limerick.”
”Tell me another one.”
”Say a Limerick.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.

des: This skill will read you a fun limerick. Just ask it to "Tell you a Limerick" or "say another one" and it will go though the 40 that is has stored. We will be adding more and more in the future!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
